quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,67,wohi to hai jis ne tum ko ( pehlay ) matti se peda kiya. phir nutfa bana kar phir lothrha bana kar phir tum ko nkalta hai ( ke tum ) bachay ( hotay ho ) phir tum apni jawani ko pahunchte ho. phir boorhay ho jatay ho. aur koi tum mein se pehlay hi mrjata hai aur tum ( mout ke ) waqt muqarrar taq poanch jatay ho aur taakay tum samjhoo
  40,68,wohi to hai jo jalataa hai aur maarta hai. phir jab woh koi kaam karna ( aur kisi ko peda karna ) chahta hai to is se keh deta hai ke hoja to woh jata hai
  40,69,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain. yeh kahan bhatak rahay hain ?
  40,70,jin logon ne kitaab ( khuda ) ko aur jo kuch hum ne payghambaroon ko day kar bheja is ko jhtlaya. woh anqareeb maloom karlen ge
  40,71,jab ke un ki gardnon mein taoq aur zanjeeren hon gi ( aur ) ghsite jayen ge
  40,72,( yani ) kholtey hue pani mein. phir aag mein jhonk diye jayen ge
  40,73,phir un se kaha jaye ga ke woh kahan hain jin ko tum ( khuda ke ) shareek banatay they
  40,74,( yani ghair khuda ) kahin ge woh to hum se jatay rahay balkay hum to pehlay kisi cheez ko pkarte hi nahi they. isi terhan khuda kafiroon ko gumraah karta hai
  40,75,yeh is ka badla hai ke tum zameen mein haq ke baghair ( yani is ke khilaaf ) khush howa karte they aur is ki ( saza hai ) ke itrayea karte they
  40,76,( ab ) jahannum ke darwazon mein daakhil hojao. hamesha isi mein raho ge. mtkbron kakiya bura thikana hai
  40,77,to ( ae paighambar ) sabr karo khuda ka wada sacha hai. agar hum tum ko kuch is mein se dikha den jis ka hum tum se wada karte hain. ( yani kafiroon par azaab nazil karen ) ya tumhari muddat hayaat poori kar dein to un ko hamari hi taraf lout kar aana hai
